data.description: Exquisite Contemporary Townhome! Step into the epitome of modern living with this impeccably designed townhome in Happy Valley. Nearly new built in 2021 and lightly lived in. Enjoy builder upgrades as well as additional dimmable lighting and ceiling fans. Inside, discover an open-concept layout that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, fostering an ideal space for entertaining guests or simply unwinding after a long day. Gather around the large island in the kitchen with food and drinks while socializing. 3 of the bedrooms and laundry all conveniently together on the upper level. Primary suite with vaulted ceilings has peak-a-boo views of Mt St Helens. Enjoy the balcony off main level with territorial views as well. 4th bedroom/bonus room on the lower level could also be a great office/den, hobby/sewing room, home gym space, only limited by your imagination. Oversized two car garage with electric opener accessed through private alley behind the townhome. Among all these great features is a tankless gas hot water system and mini-split for heating and AC. The community park is available for all residents. All common areas and landscaping covered by HOA. OPEN HOUSES 2/3 11a-1p and 2/4 12p-2p.
